   42:                     Be concise and friendly. IMPORTANT: Do NOT use Markdown formatting (like **bold** or *italics*). Use plain text only. Use dashed lists (-) for items. Ensure your response is complete and not cut off.` }],
   45:                     role: "model",
   46:                     parts: [{ text: "Hello! I am your travel assistant. I can help you find interesting temples, nature spots, and historical sites from our database. Where would you like to explore?" }],
